{"title":"编辑博客 2","uid":"f404cbaa3a1d0a8194f90fc990a59dc2","slug":"Edit Blog-2","date":"2023-02-22T05:42:00.000Z","updated":"2023-02-21T05:17:20.774Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Edit Blog-2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/jankin12138/IMG@main/img/39_white2_4k.15blza0c8sww.webp","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"博客的特殊情况\"><a href=\"#博客的特殊情况\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"博客的特殊情况\"></a>博客的特殊情况</h2><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>如果你像我一样，重装了系统，又保留了整个博客的文件，但是gitbash无法启动</p>\n<p>不必重新安装，可以在gitbash 输入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-cli -g save</code></pre>\n\n<p>即可</p>\n\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"杂七杂八的BUG\"><a href=\"#杂七杂八的BUG\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"杂七杂八的BUG\"></a>杂七杂八的BUG</h2><h3 id=\"BUG1-超链接溢出盒子\"><a href=\"#BUG1-超链接溢出盒子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG1 超链接溢出盒子\"></a>BUG1 超链接溢出盒子</h3><div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">超链接溢出盒子</p>\n<p>这个问题在移动端中尤为明显。目前无法完全解决，建议解决方案为，将原超链接改为：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-code\" data-language=\"code\"><code class=\"language-code\">[标题](链接)</code></pre>\n\n<p>的markdowm语法形式即可</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"BUG2-预览文字溢出盒子\"><a href=\"#BUG2-预览文字溢出盒子\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG2 预览文字溢出盒子\"></a>BUG2 预览文字溢出盒子</h3><div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">某网友说</p>\n<p>本博客文章底部，评论区附近的“上&#x2F;下一篇文章”处，预览文字会导致盒子高度不一样，可以在文章的md文件开头，通过 <strong>控制预览文字长度</strong> 的 <strong>preview</strong> 来解决，举例：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markdown\" data-language=\"markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">preview: 120 #控制预览文字长度\nabstracts: &quot;分享....&quot; #自定义预览文字</code></pre>\n\n<p>但我个人觉得这个BUG影响不大，可改可不改</p>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3 id=\"BUG3-缺乏JSON文件\"><a href=\"#BUG3-缺乏JSON文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BUG3 缺乏JSON文件\"></a>BUG3 缺乏JSON文件</h3><p>网友反应，有时候版本不一，或者因为其他奇怪操作之下，会出现缺乏blog-author.json的BUG</p>\n<details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>隐藏内容</summary>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Edit%20Blog/009.png\" alt=\"009\"></p>\n</details>\n<p>这时候只需要原地复制一份 public&#x2F;api&#x2F;author里面的 xxx.json ，更名为  <strong>blog-author.json</strong> 即可解决问题</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">提示</p>\n<p>此问题一般可通过版本更新来解决</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">待考证</p>\n<p>某网友说要更新npm的才行，github上面的不行</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data